getPosition

public int getPosition()
Gets position on the tape.

Returns:
The position of the head on the tape. Position zero is the leftmost position.

move

public void move(int movement)
Moves the head by movement. If the head is moved past the leftmost position, it is reset to the leftmost position.

Parameters:
movement - The amount of movement. If negative, moves to the left, and if positive, moves to the right.
